v3.0.0 — OPS Promotion Schema
=============================

Directories (Git/KV)
- /staging/<GPT>/<version>/     # candidate inputs
- /canon/<GPT>/<version>/       # immutable, approved outputs
- /logs/<GPT>/                  # reports and summaries
- /failed_promotions/           # archived failure bundles

Promotion Flow
1) Place candidate assets in /staging/<GPT>/<version>/
2) Run QGate T1→T3 and emit Loader + QGate reports
3) If PASS: open Promotion PR to main (canon)
4) On merge: move assets to /canon; append CHANGELOG; store Promotion Summary
5) If FAIL: move to /failed_promotions/ with reason + pointers; do not touch canon

Rollback
- Revert to last PASS canon directory; record rollback_ref in summary
- Never rewrite history; append new logs describing the action

Version Bumps
- patch: backward-compatible fixes/content changes
- minor: new capabilities or non-breaking structural shifts
- major: incompatible instruction or schema changes
